msgid "Moderation"
msgstr ""

#: src/contributors/05-federation.md:812
msgid ""
"These actions can only be done by instance admins or community moderators. "
"They are sent to the community and announced by it. See [](../users/04-"
"moderation.md) for a general overview how moderation works in Lemmy. "
"Communities can only be created on the same instance where a user is "
"registered. After that, mods from other instances can be added with `Add/"
"User` activity."
msgstr ""

